    "client_msg_id": "77b551e8-5a5a-40b4-a23c-5f900faa9038",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "A quick addition regarding the supremacy of plain text: No one has mentioned Unix. The \"Unix Programming Environment\" has completely dominated the programming industry. Text files are a core tenet of Unix (e.g., <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unix_philosophy>).\n\nUnix is is just as completely unimportant in all other industries, so you don't have the supremacy of text files anywhere else.",
